{"tid":1466714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日照入機場！！！但係！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:18:40.000Z","uid":69480,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"beecdd7ea38bc2d22a43088ea47ed835e457c88d","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"大家都知道今日呢場打得唔好 會輸民意輸輿論<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要贏 就要爭取番民意 國際輿論！<br />\n聽日入機場 就係道歉運動 繼續和理非</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">離境</span></span></strong> 限制人流 比佢地慢慢走 有足夠時間睇文宣<br />\n同旅客講造成不便 好對唔住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入境</span></strong></span> 繼續塞撚爆佢！<br />\n重申五大訴求 黑警還眼 宣傳8.18<br />\n<br />\n有鬼就隔離佢 適當制止就得 鬼唔會捉得曬！<br />\n無謂係到內耗！<br />\n<br />\n唔好再互屌！"},{"pid":"518ce17b5c2b5b8780318a2978e609c3cdadbe65","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5834d1aab79691f7b04dd3e2442111dae2e0557a","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aef933de955d0701b2e269f1f6f9a253505122f","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6a3ac43dada37aec6dab579332e30e7939bcfe8","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"194bc1f29daece9b7e45abd2863be93a7d01a411","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3a6f1273eb9ae8b62714d02e5c035ed66eb7363","tid":1466714,"uid":69480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cecab8ae706c231167225f8adcf598eeab6290cd","tid":1466714,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c